---
title: Fragrant Coconut Broccoli Stew with lentils and warm naan
description: If you're looking for a healthy and hearty meal that skips the meat but doesn't skimp on seasonings, this veggie lentil curry is one to try. Full of gorgeous greens and well-balanced flavours, this dish is definitely what you could call a one-pot wonder.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF220915_R09_W41_IE_IEXVV0089-1_KB_Main_high-b1a73fd0.jpg
